data.description: Discover the potential in this 5 bedroom, 4 bath home located in the popular neighborhood of Parks at Stonecrest. Offering a bright, open floor plan. Kitchen with granite countertops, stainless appliances, butler's pantry with walkin storage. Dining area with coffered ceilings. Perfect for gathering with everyone.  Spacious Master Suite with large Walk In closet, double vanities and jacuzzi tub and more. Roomy secondary bedrooms include two that share a hallway bathroom with double vanities. Upstairs, enjoy a large open space for a lounge area. This property provides versatility for multi-generational living, potential rentals, or even a home business setup. Customize the space to suit your needs and preferences.  Embrace the tranquility of the neighborhood while being conveniently located to amenities, schools, and more. Easy access to I-20!
